<head>
    <style>
        body{
            background-color: #2C3333;
            color: #E7F6F2;
        }
        a{
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            display:block;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #395B64;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 7px 4px rgb(38, 44, 44);
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            position: absolute;
            margin: 0;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            -ms-transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
        }

        .button{
            background-color: #009911;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 4px 2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h2><b>Bem-vindo(a) ao Sistema Médico</b></h2>
        <p>Para começar, clique em um dos botões abaixo.</p>
        <a href="/pacientes" class="btn btn-primary">
            <span class="button">Pacientes</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/medicos" class="btn btn-primary">
            <span class="button">Medicos</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/consulta" class="btn btn-primary">
            <span class="button">Consultas</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>